  "description": "The release of the Rube Goldberg machine puzzler <i>The Incredible Machine</i> for 3DO compiles levels from the <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/dos/incredible-machine\">original game</a> and <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/dos/even-more-incredible-machine\">its expansion</a>, adds new ones of its own and presents everything in its own graphical style.<br><br>Included are most (or all) of the 160 puzzles from the computer versions, along with many new ones for a total of 208 levels. Also available are 30 additional tutorial levels that teach the use of the basic machine parts. The &quot;Make A Machine&quot; mode allows players to construct their own machines from all available parts. These can be saved to the 3DO's internal memory for later use.",
